Programme & Operations Coordinator | Data & Reporting Systems

8 years in operations across NGO, public, and private-sector environments, including 3 years coordinating EU-funded programmes (Erasmus+, European Solidarity Corps, NIW). Reporting systems, compliance tracking, and
monitoring frameworks built from the ground up across several organisations.

This portfolio extends that work rather than departing from it. The reporting infrastructure, compliance tracking, and KPI systems I've built are the same structures analysts operate within — this is that work formalised into the analysis itself.

Background: B.Eng, Igor Sikorsky Kyiv Polytechnic Institute. C1 English.

